{"tid":800052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[讓數字說話]整理左成個8月既雨量記錄","createTime":"2018-08-30T14:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T14:30:24.000Z","uid":12599,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9eb0a9f317d11c6d2b60ee69d49a9e12134c752","tid":800052,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"有興趣既朋友可以自己分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1-WeOEV6L2hSXohlhnOfC5RKU9HKEZeb5eC9G5fwZ69Q/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1-WeOEV6L2hSXohlhnOfC5RKU9HKEZeb5eC9G5fwZ69Q%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=NQRpmiJNK76EDsQIlzutQTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=9f94b905\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1-WeOEV6L2hSXohlhnOfC5RKU9HKEZeb5eC9G5fwZ69Q/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n成個8月到呢一個moment應該有10場有暴雨警告既雨<br />\n<br />\n8月11號同20號兩場7點-8點既雨應該夠曬數出紅雨, 11號果場仲差唔多到黑雨級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然啦,係大交合角度,落到水浸都係得黃雨,係好正常既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ndata source: <a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/wr/201808/15.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fwr%2F201808%2F15.htm&d=NQRpmiJNK76EDsQIlzutQTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7794c18f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/wr/201808/15.htm</a>"}]}